---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  title="Privacy Policy — Real Tip Calculator"
  description="Real Tip Calculator privacy policy. We don't collect personal data. Learn what information we use and how we protect your privacy."
  canonicalPath="/privacy-policy"
  breadcrumb="Privacy Policy"
>
  <article class="prose">
    <span class="last-updated">Last updated: June 9, 2025 · Effective: June 9, 2025</span>

    <div class="highlight-box">
      <p><strong>Short version:</strong> Real Tip Calculator does not collect, store, or sell any personal information. All calculations happen locally in your browser. We don't even have a user database.</p>
    </div>

    <h2>1. Who We Are</h2>
    <p>
      Real Tip Calculator ("we", "our", "us") operates the website located at
      <strong>realtipcalculator.com</strong>. This Privacy Policy explains our practices regarding
      information collection and use when you visit our website.
    </p>

    <h2>2. Information We Do NOT Collect</h2>
    <p>We do not collect:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Your name, email address, or any contact information</li>
      <li>Your bill amounts, tip calculations, or financial data</li>
      <li>Account credentials (we have no user accounts)</li>
      <li>Payment information of any kind</li>
      <li>Location data beyond general country-level (via analytics)</li>
    </ul>
    <p>All tip calculations are performed entirely in your browser. No calculation data is ever sent to our servers.</p>

    <h2>3. Information That May Be Collected Automatically</h2>
    <h3>3.1 Usage Analytics</h3>
    <p>
      We may use anonymous, aggregated analytics to understand how visitors use our site
      (e.g., which pages are popular, general geographic region, browser type). This data
      cannot be used to identify individual users and is not linked to any personal information.
    </p>
    <h3>3.2 Log Data</h3>
    <p>
      Like most websites, our hosting server automatically records standard log data, including:
      IP address (anonymised), browser type, pages visited, and time of visit. This data is
      used solely for security monitoring and is automatically deleted after 30 days.
    </p>
    <h3>3.3 Local Storage</h3>
    <p>
      We store your dark/light mode preference in your browser's <code>localStorage</code>.
      This data never leaves your device and is not accessible to us.
    </p>

    <h2>4. Cookies</h2>
    <p>
      Real Tip Calculator uses minimal cookies. We may use:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Essential cookies</strong> — required for the website to function (e.g., theme preference)</li>
      <li><strong>Analytics cookies</strong> — anonymous usage statistics (if analytics are enabled)</li>
    </ul>
    <p>We do not use advertising, tracking, or third-party marketing cookies.</p>

    <h2>5. Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>We may use the following third-party services:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Google Fonts</strong> — to load web fonts (Inter, Manrope, DM Sans). Google may log font requests per their own privacy policy.</li>
      <li><strong>Hosting provider</strong> — our website is hosted on a third-party server that processes standard web traffic logs.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>We do not use Google Ads, Facebook Pixel, or any advertising networks.</p>

    <h2>6. Children's Privacy</h2>
    <p>
      Real Tip Calculator does not knowingly collect information from children under 13 years of age.
      Our service is a general-purpose calculator tool suitable for all ages.
    </p>

    <h2>7. Data Security</h2>
    <p>
      Since we do not collect personal data, there is no personal data to secure or breach.
      Your calculations remain entirely on your own device.
    </p>

    <h2>8. Your Rights</h2>
    <p>Since we do not collect personal data, standard data rights requests (access, deletion, portability) are not applicable. However, if you have questions, please <a href="/contact">contact us</a>.</p>

    <h2>9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>
      We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page
      with a revised "Last updated" date. Continued use of the site after changes constitutes
      acceptance of the updated policy.
    </p>

    <h2>10. Contact</h2>
    <p>
      If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please visit our <a href="/contact">Contact page</a>.
    </p>
  </article>
</PageLayout>
